          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I work out the right ring size?",
            "answer": "<p>Need sizing help or advice on keeping it a secret? Email us at <strong>info@thepromiseco.com</strong> and we can help you figure out a ring size.</p><p>We recommend ordering a standard ring sizer from Amazon, they usually look like a key chain with lots of metal rings. Once you've got your size you can use our handy guide below to convert it, or email us for help.</p><p>Use our <a href=\"/pages/ring-size-guide\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ring Size Guide\">size guide</a> to find your perfect fit</p><p></p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_39kHFp": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I don't know which ring to pick for a gift?",
            "answer": "<p>If you need personalised support on picking the perfect ring, email our team at <strong>info@thepromiseco.com</strong> and we will do our best to support.</p><p>Alternatively, shop our <a href=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/products/the-promise-ring-co-e-gift-card\" title=\"The Promise Ring Co. E-Gift Card\">E-Gift cards</a>, for the perfect fit, everytime.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_k8h6gB": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is my ring under warranty?",
            "answer": "<p>At The Promise Ring Co. we are committed to providing you with<br/>exceptional service and ensuring that your purchase of your ring is a truly special and sentimental experience. We understand that these pieces aren't just jewellery; they are symbols of love, commitment, and cherished moments.</p><p>That's why we stand by our products and offer a 2-year guarantee to give you peace of mind.</p><p>For full warranty terms <a href=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\">click here</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_VnPF3N": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I've damaged my special ring, what can I do?",
            "answer": "<p>We understand accidents happen and we know how precious all our pieces are to each customer.</p><p>Email us a picture of the damage to <strong>info@thepromiseco.com </strong>and we will do our best to support you with solutions</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_zibkrY": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I need an urgent gift but your delivery doesn't work for me...",
            "answer": "<p>Looking for the perfect gift for your last minute woes, shop our <a href=\"https://thepromiseringco.com/products/the-promise-ring-co-e-gift-card\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Promise Ring Co. E-Gift Card\">E-gift cards </a>for the perfect fit, everytime.</p>"
          }
        }
